/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main><section class=\"section-compact\"><div class=\"container-page\"><div class=\"grid items-center gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]\"><div class=\"relative min-h-[390px] overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain object-left-bottom\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"52vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-full-cover.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"text-right\"><nav class=\"mb-4 text-xs font-bold text-muted\"><a href=\"/\">الرئيسية</a><span class=\"mx-2 text-[#A7815E]\">›</span>إضافة أصل عقاري</nav><h1 class=\"font-display text-[clamp(2.2rem,4.2vw,4.25rem)] font-black leading-[1.35] text-[#1D1916]\">إضافة أصل عقاري</h1><p class=\"mt-4 font-display text-2xl font-extrabold leading-10 text-[#A7815E]\">ابدأ رحلة تطوير أصلك العقاري وتحويله إلى فرصة استثمارية أو مساهمة عقارية منظمة.</p><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm font-bold leading-8 text-muted\">أدخل بيانات الأصل العقاري وسيتولى فريق مهابة دراسة وتحليل فرص التطوير والاستثمار.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-6\"><ol class=\"grid gap-3 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-4 md:grid-cols-5\"><li class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"mx-auto grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full border text-sm font-black border-[#A7815E] bg-[#F6EDE4] text-[#8F6B4C]\">01</span><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-[#8F6B4C]\">بيانات الملكية</p></li><li class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"mx-auto grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full border text-sm font-black border-line bg-white text-muted\">02</span><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">بيانات الأصل</p></li><li class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"mx-auto grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full border text-sm font-black border-line bg-white text-muted\">03</span><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">الموقع</p></li><li class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"mx-auto grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full border text-sm font-black border-line bg-white text-muted\">04</span><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">المرفقات</p></li><li class=\"text-center\"><span class=\"mx-auto grid h-12 w-12 place-items-center rounded-full border text-sm font-black border-line bg-white text-muted\">05</span><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">المراجعة والإرسال</p></li></ol></div></div></section><section class=\"section-compact\"><div class=\"container-page\"><form><div class=\"grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_250px]\"><div class=\"space-y-5 rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/78 p-5\"><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-headphones h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3\"></path></svg> بيانات التواصل</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">الاسم الكامل *<input required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"أدخل الاسم الكامل\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"fullName\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">رقم الجوال *<input required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"05xxxxxxxx\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"mobile\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">البريد الإلكتروني *<input required=\"\" type=\"email\" placeholder=\"example@domain.com\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"email\"/></label></div></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg> بيانات الملكية (الصك)</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">رقم الصك *<input required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"أدخل رقم الصك\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"deedNumber\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">تاريخ الصك *<input required=\"\" type=\"date\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"deedDate\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">مساحة الصك (م²) *<input required=\"\" type=\"number\" placeholder=\"أدخل مساحة الصك\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"area\"/></label></div><p class=\"mt-3 rounded-md bg-[#F6EDE4] px-4 py-3 text-xs font-bold text-[#8F6B4C]\">نأمل إدخال رقم الصك وتاريخ الصك بدقة لضمان دراسة أصلك العقاري بشكل صحيح.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg> بيانات الأصل العقاري</h2><div class=\"mb-4 grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6\"><label class=\"flex h-16 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-3 text-center text-xs font-extrabold border-line bg-white text-[#1D1916]\"><input class=\"sr-only\" type=\"radio\" name=\"assetType\" value=\"أرض خام\"/>أرض خام</label><label class=\"flex h-16 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-3 text-center text-xs font-extrabold border-[#A7815E] bg-[#F6EDE4] text-[#8F6B4C]\"><input class=\"sr-only\" type=\"radio\" name=\"assetType\" checked=\"\" value=\"أرض سكنية\"/>أرض سكنية</label><label class=\"flex h-16 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-3 text-center text-xs font-extrabold border-line bg-white text-[#1D1916]\"><input class=\"sr-only\" type=\"radio\" name=\"assetType\" value=\"أرض تجارية\"/>أرض تجارية</label><label class=\"flex h-16 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-3 text-center text-xs font-extrabold border-line bg-white text-[#1D1916]\"><input class=\"sr-only\" type=\"radio\" name=\"assetType\" value=\"أرض صناعية\"/>أرض صناعية</label><label class=\"flex h-16 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-3 text-center text-xs font-extrabold border-line bg-white text-[#1D1916]\"><input class=\"sr-only\" type=\"radio\" name=\"assetType\" value=\"أصل قائم\"/>أصل قائم</label><label class=\"flex h-16 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-3 text-center text-xs font-extrabold border-line bg-white text-[#1D1916]\"><input class=\"sr-only\" type=\"radio\" name=\"assetType\" value=\"مشروع متعثر\"/>مشروع متعثر</label></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr]\"><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">اسم الأصل (اختياري)<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"أدخل اسم الأصل\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"assetName\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">وصف الأصل *<input required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"أدخل وصفاً مختصراً عن الأصل وميزاته وإمكانات التطوير أو الاستثمار.\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"description\"/></label></div><div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-4 rounded-md border border-line bg-white p-4 text-sm font-bold text-muted\"><span class=\"text-[#1D1916]\">الواجهة *</span><label class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"accent-[#A7815E]\" name=\"frontage\" checked=\"\"/>شمالية</label><label class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"accent-[#A7815E]\" name=\"frontage\"/>جنوبية</label><label class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"accent-[#A7815E]\" name=\"frontage\"/>شرقية</label><label class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"accent-[#A7815E]\" name=\"frontage\"/>غربية</label></div></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg> الموقع</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr]\"><div class=\"relative min-h-[170px] overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-line bg-[#D9D1C7]\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-65 grayscale-[8%] sepia-[8%]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"45vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fknowledge-library.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 h-10 w-10 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 fill-[#A7815E] text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div class=\"grid gap-4\"><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">المدينة *<select required=\"\" name=\"city\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition focus:border-[#A7815E]\"><option value=\"\" disabled=\"\" selected=\"\">اختر</option><option value=\"الرياض\">الرياض</option><option value=\"جدة\">جدة</option><option value=\"الدمام\">الدمام</option><option value=\"الخبر\">الخبر</option><option value=\"مكة\">مكة</option><option value=\"المدينة المنورة\">المدينة المنورة</option></select></label><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">الحي *<input required=\"\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"اختر الحي\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"district\"/></label><label class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">رابط الموقع (اختياري)<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"https://maps.google.com\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-line bg-white px-4 text-sm font-bold outline-none transition placeholder:text-muted/55 focus:border-[#A7815E]\" name=\"mapUrl\"/></label></div></div></section><section><h2 class=\"mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 font-display text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cloud-upload h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 13v8\"></path><path d=\"M4 14.899A7 7 0 1 1 15.71 8h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 2.5 8.242\"></path><path d=\"m8 17 4-4 4 4\"></path></svg> المرفقات</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4\"><label class=\"grid min-h-[110px] cursor-pointer place-items-center rounded-md border border-dashed border-[#A7815E]/45 bg-white p-4 text-center transition hover:bg-[#fff7ef]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cloud-upload h-8 w-8 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 13v8\"></path><path d=\"M4 14.899A7 7 0 1 1 15.71 8h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 2.5 8.242\"></path><path d=\"m8 17 4-4 4 4\"></path></svg><span class=\"mt-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">صورة الصك<!-- --> *</span><span class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-muted\">JPG, PNG, PDF - الحد الأقصى 10MB</span><input type=\"file\" class=\"sr-only\" multiple=\"\" required=\"\" name=\"files\"/></label><label class=\"grid min-h-[110px] cursor-pointer place-items-center rounded-md border border-dashed border-[#A7815E]/45 bg-white p-4 text-center transition hover:bg-[#fff7ef]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cloud-upload h-8 w-8 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 13v8\"></path><path d=\"M4 14.899A7 7 0 1 1 15.71 8h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 2.5 8.242\"></path><path d=\"m8 17 4-4 4 4\"></path></svg><span class=\"mt-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">مخطط الأرض</span><span class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-muted\">JPG, PNG, PDF - الحد الأقصى 10MB</span><input type=\"file\" class=\"sr-only\" multiple=\"\" name=\"files\"/></label><label class=\"grid min-h-[110px] cursor-pointer place-items-center rounded-md border border-dashed border-[#A7815E]/45 bg-white p-4 text-center transition hover:bg-[#fff7ef]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cloud-upload h-8 w-8 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 13v8\"></path><path d=\"M4 14.899A7 7 0 1 1 15.71 8h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 2.5 8.242\"></path><path d=\"m8 17 4-4 4 4\"></path></svg><span class=\"mt-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">صور الأصل</span><span class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-muted\">JPG, PNG, PDF - الحد الأقصى 10MB</span><input type=\"file\" class=\"sr-only\" multiple=\"\" name=\"files\"/></label><label class=\"grid min-h-[110px] cursor-pointer place-items-center rounded-md border border-dashed border-[#A7815E]/45 bg-white p-4 text-center transition hover:bg-[#fff7ef]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cloud-upload h-8 w-8 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 13v8\"></path><path d=\"M4 14.899A7 7 0 1 1 15.71 8h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 2.5 8.242\"></path><path d=\"m8 17 4-4 4 4\"></path></svg><span class=\"mt-2 text-sm font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">ملفات إضافية</span><span class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] font-bold text-muted\">JPG, PNG, PDF - الحد الأقصى 10MB</span><input type=\"file\" class=\"sr-only\" multiple=\"\" name=\"files\"/></label></div></section><section class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white p-5\"><h2 class=\"mb-3 flex items-center gap-2 font-display text-xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check h-5 w-5 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> المراجعة والإرسال</h2><label class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm font-bold leading-7 text-muted\"><input required=\"\" type=\"checkbox\" class=\"mt-1 accent-[#A7815E]\"/>أقر أن جميع البيانات المدخلة صحيحة.</label><label class=\"mt-2 flex items-start gap-3 text-sm font-bold leading-7 text-muted\"><input required=\"\" type=\"checkbox\" class=\"mt-1 accent-[#A7815E]\"/>أوافق على الشروط والأحكام وسياسة الخصوصية.</label></section><div class=\"grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3\"><button type=\"submit\" value=\"draft\" class=\"h-12 rounded-md border border-[#A7815E]/45 bg-white text-sm font-extrabold text-[#8F6B4C] disabled:opacity-60\" name=\"intent\">حفظ كمسودة</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-[#A7815E]/45 bg-white text-sm font-extrabold text-[#8F6B4C]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg> معاينة الطلب</button><button type=\"submit\" value=\"submit\" class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-[#A7815E] text-sm font-extrabold text-white disabled:opacity-60\" name=\"intent\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg>إرسال للمراجعة</button></div></div><aside class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/78 p-5\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">ملخص الطلب</h2><p class=\"mt-3 border-b border-line pb-2 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">- <!-- -->بيانات الملكية</p><p class=\"mt-3 border-b border-line pb-2 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">- <!-- -->بيانات الأصل</p><p class=\"mt-3 border-b border-line pb-2 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">- <!-- -->الموقع</p><p class=\"mt-3 border-b border-line pb-2 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">- <!-- -->المرفقات</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">عدد الملفات <span class=\"text-[#1D1916]\">0</span></p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/78 p-5\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">لماذا إضافة الأصل عبر مهابة؟</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">• <!-- -->دراسة الجدوى</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">• <!-- -->الهيكلة والتنظيم</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">• <!-- -->الحوكمة والامتثال</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">• <!-- -->تعظيم القيمة</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm font-bold text-muted\">• <!-- -->الوصول للمستثمرين</p></div></aside></div></form></div></section><section class=\"section-compact\"><div class=\"container-page\"><h2 class=\"mb-5 text-center font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#1D1916] gold-divider\">ماذا يحدث بعد الإرسال؟</h2><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clipboard-check mx-auto h-10 w-10 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"8\" height=\"4\" x=\"8\" y=\"2\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><path d=\"m9 14 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">مراجعة البيانات</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-bold leading-7 text-muted\">يقوم فريق مهابة بمراجعة البيانات والتأكد من اكتمالها.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 mx-auto h-10 w-10 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">تحليل الأصل</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-bold leading-7 text-muted\">يتم دراسة الأصل وتحليل فرص التطوير والاستثمار المتاحة.</p></article><article class=\"rounded-lg border border-line bg-white/72 p-5 text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-headphones mx-auto h-10 w-10 text-[#A7815E]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-[#1D1916]\">التواصل معك</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs font-bold leading-7 text-muted\">يتواصل معك فريق مهابة لمناقشة النتائج والخطوات التالية.</p></article></div><div class=\"relative mt-8 overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-line bg-[#F6F4F1] p-6 text-center\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-25 grayscale-[8%] sepia-[8%]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Ffinal-cta-map-building.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-3xl font-extra